		 	<span id="comment_score_64355946" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64355946); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~cascadingstylesheet">cascadingstylesheet</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~cascadingstylesheet">( 140919 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64355946">		
		on Saturday March 30, 2024 @09:11AM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23273962&amp;cid=64355946">#64355946</a>)
		<small><a href="//slashdot.org/~cascadingstylesheet/journal/" title="Tuesday May 04, 2021 @11:02PM" class="user_journal_display">Journal</a> </small>
</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64355946"><p>We now engage in "morality theater".
</p><p>Since we threw out, you know, <i>actual</i> morality, we now have to make up a bunch of new ad hoc rules, which we are as zealous about enforcing as anyone ever was.
p.Prepare to get the scarlet "U" ("un-woke"?) if you use an image of a woman with a bare shoulder wearing a hat.</p></div>
	</div>

