		<div id="comment_body_64356526"><p>I'll note that there are many jobs that are almost entirely men, that you don't hear complaints about there not being enough women - garbage collectors and such.</p><p>I'm going to note here that "feminists" are not some sort of universal standardized body.  You have everything from first generation feminists to TERFs.  As such, you have people with radically different ideas of "Equality", and there's even those who think that women should be superior.</p><p>But, in general, you see at least some women complaining becaus<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64356526">

